</text>
<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Arab Studies Minor is an interdisciplinary minor that allows students to learn about the pre-modern and modern history, cultures, societies, and diasporas of Arabic-speaking peoples of West Asia and North Africa as well as other users of Arabic. The Arab Studies Minor is open to undergraduates in all four colleges.</p>
<h2>Minor Advisor</h2>
<p><a href="https://mesa.ucdavis.edu/advising-office">Middle East/South Asia Studies Advising Office</a></p>
]]>
</informationtext>
