<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Arab Studies minor covers an area of historical, cultural, economic, and geopolitical significance. Several key contemporary issues make the region as a whole a focus of interest for scholarly study.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
